OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Series of failings
OL,4,Cin killer's care revealed in new report
OL,6,FA report has revealed triple killer
OL,7,FValdo Calocane was not forced to have
OL,8,Flong-lasting antipsychotic medication
OL,9,Fbecause he did not like needles.
OL,11,FCalocane, who had been diagnosed with
OL,12,Fparanoid schizophrenia, was sentenced
OL,13,Fto an indefinite hospital order after
OL,14,Fkilling 19-year-old students Barnaby
OL,15,FWebber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar and 65-
OL,16,Fyear-old caretaker Ian Coates before
OL,17,Fattempting to kill three other people
OL,18,Fin June 2023.
