OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Series of failings
OL,4,Cin killer's care revealed in new report
OL,6,FNHS England commissioned Theemis
OL,7,FConsulting to carry out an independent
OL,8,Finvestigation into the care and
OL,9,Ftreatment provided to Calocane by NHS
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FThe document detailed a number of
OL,13,Fincidents involving patients linked to
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust.
