OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Series of failings
OL,4,Cin killer's care revealed in new report
OL,6,FThe report said: "Between 2019 and
OL,7,F2023 there were 15 incidents of
OL,8,Fpatients either under the current care
OL,9,Fof the trust or who had been
OL,10,Fdischarged from the trust,
OL,11,Fperpetrating serious violence towards
OL,12,Fmembers of the community".
OL,14,FWhile some of the victims were known
OL,15,Fto perpetrators, in some incidents,
OL,16,Fthe victims "appeared to be strangers".
OL,18,F"The level of violence in the
OL,19,Fincidents was extremely serious and in
OL,20,Fthree cases resulted in fatalities,"
OL,21,Fthe report said.
