OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Series of failings
OL,4,Cin killer's care revealed in new report
OL,6,F"The majority of these incidents
OL,7,Finvolved stabbings.
OL,9,F"Most notably, in February 2023 there
OL,10,Fwas an incident where a patient in
OL,11,Freceipt of mental health services from
OL,12,FNottingham Healthcare NHS Trust was
OL,13,Farrested for stabbing five people over
OL,14,Fthe course of a weekend."
OL,16,FThe review team checked to see if the
OL,17,Ftrust board had discussed these
OL,18,Fincidents but found "limited evidence
OL,19,Fregarding discussions of these
OL,20,Fparticular serious incidents or
OL,21,Fsubsequent investigations."
