OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Series of failings
OL,4,Cin killer's care revealed in new report
OL,6,FThe report detailed failures in risk
OL,7,Fassessments made by those caring for
OL,8,FCalocane.
OL,10,FIt was revealed the risk to staff who
OL,11,Flooked after him was "managed" by
OL,12,Fmaking arrangements so workers didn't
OL,13,Fvisit his home alone, but they didn't
OL,14,Fplan for the "hazards" if he came off
OL,15,Fhis medication and disengaged with
OL,16,Fmental health services.
