OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Series of failings
OL,4,Cin killer's care revealed in new report
OL,6,FThe report detailed two years of
OL,7,Fviolent and disturbing behaviour from
OL,8,FCalocane, including frightening a
OL,9,Fneighbour so much she jumped out of a
OL,10,Ffirst-floor window, leading to a
OL,11,Fserious back injury, punching a police
OL,12,Fofficer in the face and holding his
OL,13,Fflatmates "hostage".
OL,15,FIt added the family of Calocane's
OL,16,Fvoice "was not effectively considered"
OL,17,Fwhen judging how dangerous he was.
OL,19,FOverall, it found risk "was not fully
OL,20,Funderstood, managed, documented or
OL,21,Fcommunicated".
