OL,3,CNottingham attacks: Series of failings
OL,4,Cin killer's care revealed in new report
OL,6,F"Most of the document is cut and
OL,7,Fpasted from the previous care plan
OL,8,Fcompleted at the first admission... no
OL,9,Ffurther risk assessments were
OL,10,Fcompleted during his inpatient stay or
OL,11,Fupon discharge," according to the
OL,12,Freport.
OL,14,FIt also highlighted how Calocane's
OL,15,Ffamily was concerned his second
OL,16,Fhospital admission was only two weeks
OL,17,Flong, and such a short stay was a
OL,18,F"missed opportunity to fully
OL,19,Funderstand (Calocane's) diagnosis,
OL,20,Frisk and to get to grips with a
OL,21,Ftreatment plan".
