OL,7,Fmuch of his medication Calocane was
OL,8,Ftaking, and didn't force him to have
OL,9,Flong-lasting antipsychotic medication,
OL,10,Fbecause he didn't like needles.
OL,12,FInvestigators said NHS England should
OL,13,Fexamine the "dissonance between what
OL,14,Fpeople think should be happening, for
OL,15,Fexample, care described in national
OL,16,Fpolicies and guidance, compared to
OL,17,Fwhat is actually being delivered in
OL,18,Fsome services".
