OL,6,FThey highlighted Calocane was
OL,7,Fdischarged without a face-to-face
OL,8,Fmeeting, a practice the which they say
OL,9,Fcreated "the potential for greater
OL,10,Frisk to the person using mental health
OL,11,Fservices and to others".
OL,13,FThe report also found he was
OL,14,Fdischarged from community services
OL,15,Fback to his GP for not turning up to
OL,16,Fappointments.
OL,18,FThe authors said a lack of engagement
OL,19,Fhad become an "accepted reason for
OL,20,Fdischarge" and "normalised".
