OL,6,FThey found "trust oversight did not
OL,7,Fsufficiently alert the Trust to the
OL,8,Fnormalisation of a compromised
OL,9,Fdelivery of care."
OL,11,FThe trust has been approached for
OL,12,Fcomment.
OL,14,FThe families of the victims of the
OL,15,FNottingham attacks said: "It is the
OL,16,Ffirst duty of the Government to keep
OL,17,Fits citizens safe ` it is now clear
OL,18,Fthat the previous Government failed
OL,19,FGrace, Barnaby and Ian in that duty.
