OL,6,F"It's clear the system got it wrong"
OL,8,FNHS officials published the full
OL,9,Freport after initially saying they
OL,10,Fwould only publish a summary due to
OL,11,Fdata protection issues.
OL,13,FDr Jessica Sokolov, regional medical
OL,14,Fdirector at NHS England (Midlands),
OL,15,Fsaid: "It's clear the system got it
OL,16,Fwrong, including the NHS, and the
OL,17,Fconsequences of when this happens can
OL,18,Fbe devastating.
